{"tid":18350,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"小島秀夫新作《 Death Stranding 》最新 Trailer","createTime":"2016-12-02T08:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T14:04:08.000Z","uid":4044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"550f854f5b4125fc9a8a55c31bce2169ef37bc19","tid":18350,"uid":4044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:48:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H2Hy96sOnq8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DH2Hy96sOnq8&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=20e04601\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H2Hy96sOnq8</a><br />\n<br />\n　　由知名遊戲創作者小島秀夫領軍的新生小島工作室（Kojima Production）製作，預定在 PS4 / PC 推出的新類型動作遊戲《死亡之絆（Death Stranding）》，在方才舉辦的「The Game Awards 2016」頒獎典禮上，公布了最新宣傳影片，確認《環太平洋》導演吉勒摩‧戴托羅（Guillermo del Toro）與《雙面人魔》主角漢尼拔演員麥斯‧米克森（Mads Mikkelsen）將會參與遊戲的演出。<br />\n <br />\n目前已知將參與《死亡之絆》演出的包括最初的預告影片揭露的《陰屍路》演員諾曼&middot;李杜斯（Norman Reedus），以及這次揭露的《環太平洋》導演吉勒摩‧戴托羅與《雙面人魔》演員麥斯‧米克森。李杜斯與戴托羅先前曾在《沉默之丘》系列新作互動預告片《P.T.》中與小島秀夫合作，如今則是把合作關係延伸到小島單飛後的首款新作《死亡之絆》中，還加上近年來以電視劇《雙面人魔》中的食人魔漢尼拔與《奇異博士》中的大反派卡西流斯廣為人知的丹麥演員米克森。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3j0qrxhb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3j0qrxhb&h=698ba724&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麥斯‧米克森（Mads Mikkelsen）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/z7h269be\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fz7h269be&h=45db036d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吉勒摩‧戴托羅（Guillermo del Toro）<br />\n<br />\n此外，在美國時間 12 月 3、4 日舉辦的 PlayStation 年度玩家活動「PlayStation Experience 2016」中，小島秀夫將與未公布的特別來賓共同參與《死亡之絆》的主題講座。從這次公布的宣傳影片來看，很有可能會邀請李杜斯、戴托羅或米克森擔任特別來賓，有興趣的玩家不妨多多留意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c003e9d7852109a410b530ce2f99c8ce8c011bc3","tid":18350,"uid":4044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:52:12.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H2Hy96sOnq8[/url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DH2Hy96sOnq8%5B%2Furl&d=EHipY5QqnFkcHnyd5ykVzEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=5de98339\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H2Hy96sOnq8[/url</a>"},{"pid":"33aee95c0ebb265432acbddea7e922cef702bccc","tid":18350,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:58:05.000Z","msg":"dr hannibal <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d66fd2915bac0815972db2ca5c3d93a39011a59","tid":18350,"uid":24935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:21:25.000Z","msg":"小島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2751be9082da861e49a241108609370bfabb1372","tid":18350,"uid":51521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T10:41:21.000Z","msg":"就快j撚爆我"},{"pid":"61e698d51587388e0cb772a3827a0f3eda0c9d55","tid":18350,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T10:56:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"623a773ed482ce11be99e67b24205c60a7f8db2a","tid":18350,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T12:31:06.000Z","msg":"😸危殆bb一鍵留名！！"},{"pid":"528c345b5cfa11ecd045bd485160e174ad571e4c","tid":18350,"uid":5724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T12:42:18.000Z","msg":"Mads<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有Norman<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知三十歲前玩